14
00:00:57,920 --> 00:00:59,876
Katrine Fønsmark.

15
00:01:00,040 --> 00:01:04,431
I have some information
you'll appreciate.

16
00:01:04,600 --> 00:01:09,230
Who is this?
- Meet me in the parking lot.

17
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:14,029
Leave it at reception.
- I want to hand it over.

18
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:18,830
Come out here alone.
