19
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:23,312
I'm leaving in five minutes.
It's up to you.

20
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:29,870
Have you got two minutes?
- Sure.

21
00:01:38,800 --> 00:01:41,633
Katrine.

22
00:01:47,240 --> 00:01:49,674
Hello.

23
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:03,633
Hello.

24
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:28,150
See anything?
- Just a silver Renault.

25
